# Security And Networking

- Communication via Cloudflare Tunnels only.
- UFW denies all inbound except LAN.
- Expose zero public ports.
- Internal telemetry and audit logging must write to `openshell_audit_logs`.
- Maintain Human-in-the-Loop visibility at all times.
